@GhubAiHub_HostAddress = http://localhost:5203
@Ollama_HostAddress = http://localhost:11434

### Get Ollama-style tags (list available models)
GET {{GhubAiHub_HostAddress}}/api/tags
Accept: application/json

###

### Get detailed registry information (nodes)
GET {{GhubAiHub_HostAddress}}/api/registry
Accept: application/json

###

### Get aggregated models (OpenAI-style)
GET {{GhubAiHub_HostAddress}}/v1/models
Accept: application/json

###

### Get aggregated models (OpenAI-style)
GET {{Ollama_HostAddress}}/v1/models
Accept: application/json

###

### OpenAI-style chat completions (streaming)
POST {{GhubAiHub_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "model": "llama3.2:latest",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Say hello and identify your model." }
  ]
}


### OpenAI-style chat completions (streaming)
POST {{Ollama_HostAddress}}/v1/chat/completions
Content-Type: application/json
Accept: text/event-stream

{
  "model": "llama3.2:latest",
  "messages": [
    { "role": "user", "content": "Say hello and identify your model." }
